Name: Shan Gui II: Sweet Osmanthus II
About the game: As the autumn comes, sweet osmanthus's fragrant is pervading Zijin Mountain again. This is an AVG game produced by Magenta Factory, follow the storyline of Shan Gui and Bai Qu , with an innovative comic book style display. The Episode 1 & 2 of the game now published. The whole story tells about He Jia and Han Hui's reunion, in the sweet and mild autumn season. You will be guided by the girls, once again, enjoy a fantastic autumn journey of the ancient Chinese city of Nanjing.
